OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776856004
OL,3,C'Slavery was never abolished':
OL,4,CDomestic workers call for visa reform
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Michael
OL,7,FMaitland-Jones
OL,9,FA group that represents over 16,000
OL,10,Foverseas domestic workers in the UK is
OL,11,Furging the government to restore
OL,12,Frights that they say will offer them
OL,13,Fmore protection from exploitation.
OL,15,FThe Voice of Domestic Workers group
OL,16,Fhas written to over 50 Labour MPs and
OL,17,Fheld a protest outside parliament on
OL,18,FMonday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
