OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776856004
OL,3,C'Slavery was never abolished':
OL,4,CDomestic workers call for visa reform
OL,6,FThe group is made up of migrant women
OL,7,Fwho are often employed by foreign
OL,8,Fbosses in the UK, working as nannies,
OL,9,Fcarers and doing household work.
OL,11,FThey are asking the government to
OL,12,Frestore rights that are tied to the
OL,13,Foverseas domestic worker (ODW) visa,
OL,14,Fwhich was introduced by the Labour
OL,15,Fgovernment in 1998.
OL,17,FIn 2012, the option to apply to renew
OL,18,Fthe visa beyond six months was
OL,19,Fremoved, along with the option to
OL,20,Fchange employer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776856004
OL,3,C'Slavery was never abolished':
OL,4,CDomestic workers call for visa reform
OL,6,FWhile some of these rights have since
OL,7,Fbeen restored, the group argues that
OL,8,Fdomestic workers remain uniquely
OL,9,Fvulnerable to many forms of abuse from
OL,10,Ftheir employers.
OL,12,F'Modern slavery'
OL,14,F"This is something that they (the
OL,15,Fgovernment) should never have swept
OL,16,Funder the carpet," said the group's
OL,17,Fhead, Marissa Begonia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776856004
OL,3,C'Slavery was never abolished':
OL,4,CDomestic workers call for visa reform
OL,6,FShe argues that the ability to renew
OL,7,Fthe ODW visa is crucial in giving
OL,8,Fworkers rights that protect them from
OL,9,Ftrafficking and sexual abuse.
OL,11,FThe government says that crimes like
OL,12,Fthis can be reported through the
OL,13,Fnational referral mechanism (NRM)
OL,14,Fframework, but Marissa argues that it
OL,15,Fis not fit for purpose.
OL,17,F"We have many cases of rape," she
OL,18,Fsays, speaking about women she has
OL,19,Fhelped support.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
