OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776856004
OL,3,C'Slavery was never abolished':
OL,4,CDomestic workers call for visa reform
OL,6,F"Slavery was never abolished... we
OL,7,Ffound many that are very skinny
OL,8,Fbecause they've been starved, they're
OL,9,Fnot being fed properly, and the
OL,10,Fmajority of them were not receiving a
OL,11,Fsalary."
OL,13,FThe 'Voice of Domestic Workers' group
OL,14,Fheld a protest outside parliament on
OL,15,FMonday
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
