OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776856004
OL,3,C'Slavery was never abolished':
OL,4,CDomestic workers call for visa reform
OL,6,FShe says giving ODWs the ability to
OL,7,Frenew visas will be "more productive
OL,8,Ffor the UK economy as domestic workers
OL,9,Fperform jobs that allow other sectors,
OL,10,Fother workers, to be able to work, to
OL,11,Ffunction".
OL,13,FShe adds that the existing system for
OL,14,Fdomestic workers "does not reduce
OL,15,Fimmigration and helps push workers
OL,16,Finto hidden, unsafe situations".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
