OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776856004
OL,3,C'Slavery was never abolished':
OL,4,CDomestic workers call for visa reform
OL,6,FIn 2016, ODWs were given more control
OL,7,Fover changing employers, but
OL,8,Fcampaigners have argued that the short-
OL,9,Fterm nature of their visas makes
OL,10,Fleaving unsuitable employers
OL,11,Fcomplicated.
OL,13,FWhat has the government said?
OL,15,FThe Home Office has acknowledged the
OL,16,Fscale of abuse faced by overseas
OL,17,Fdomestic workers in the UK, describing
OL,18,Fthem as a "distinctly vulnerable
OL,19,Fcohort".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
