PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776856004
OL,3,C'Slavery was never abolished':
OL,4,CDomestic workers call for visa reform
OL,6,FIn a statement, it said: "Too many
OL,7,Fpeople who come to the UK to work as
OL,8,Fdomestic workers are being exploited
OL,9,Fby their employers and become modern
OL,10,Fslaves.
OL,12,F"We're committed to making sure they
OL,13,Fare protected from abuse and are
OL,14,Fcurrently reviewing how their visas
OL,15,Fwork to protect them."
OL,17,FHowever, the Home Office added that
OL,18,Fsince it was due to review the nature
OL,19,Fof the ODW visa, restoring rights to
OL,20,Fhow they were prior to 2012 would not
OL,21,Fbe "appropriate" before the review.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776856004
OL,3,C'Slavery was never abolished':
OL,4,CDomestic workers call for visa reform
OL,6,F"The ODW visa only grants permission
OL,7,Ffor up to six months and cannot be
OL,8,Fextended. This visa length aligns with
OL,9,Fthat of the ODW's employer, who cannot
OL,10,Fintend to stay for longer than the six-
OL,11,Fmonth period and reflects the short-
OL,12,Fterm nature of their time in the UK."
OL,14,FIt also said that employers of ODWs
OL,15,Fmust act in accordance with UK
OL,16,Femployment law, including the National
OL,17,FMinimum Wage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
